      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great overall, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is solid\u2014it starts right up, shifts smoothly, and has a consistent service history. This is a dependable, honest vehicle that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
