      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m selling my trusty car, and it's honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend road trips. It runs like a charm and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically robust example of the legendary S54-powered chassis. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six remains a masterpiece of engineering, featuring individual throttle bodies that provide exceptional throttle response and a linear power band peaking at 7,900 RPM. This vehicle is equipped with the desirable 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a cooling system refresh utilizing an aluminum radiator to mitigate heat soak. The suspension maintains its factory-spec kinematics, offering the tactile steering feedback and lateral stability synonymous with the M division. While the exterior shows minor evidence of spirited road use, the subframe has been inspected for stress fractures and remains structurally sound. This is a high-performance machine optimized for the driving purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
